---
import DocsLayout from '../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
import { Type, Sparkles, AtSign, Link, Paperclip, Phone } from 'lucide-astro';

const entities = [
  { name: 'Bold',           type: 'bold',            extra: null,           group: 'Formatting' },
  { name: 'Italic',         type: 'italic',          extra: null,           group: 'Formatting' },
  { name: 'Underline',      type: 'underline',       extra: 'colour: number?', group: 'Formatting' },
  { name: 'Strikethrough',  type: 'strikethrough',   extra: null,           group: 'Formatting' },
  { name: 'Spoiler',        type: 'spoiler',         extra: null,           group: 'Formatting' },
  { name: 'Monospace',      type: 'monospace',       extra: null,           group: 'Formatting' },
  { name: 'Capitalized',    type: 'capitalized',     extra: null,           group: 'Formatting' },
  { name: 'Fraction',       type: 'fraction',        extra: 'numerator: number?, denominator: number?', group: 'Formatting' },
  { name: 'Ordinal',        type: 'ordinal',         extra: null,           group: 'Formatting' },

  { name: 'Mention',         type: 'mention',          extra: 'userId: string?',      group: 'Mentions' },
  { name: 'MentionEveryone', type: 'mentionEveryone',  extra: null,                   group: 'Mentions' },
  { name: 'MentionRole',     type: 'mentionRole',      extra: 'archetypeId: string?', group: 'Mentions' },

  { name: 'Url',      type: 'url',      extra: 'domain: string, path: string', group: 'Links' },
  { name: 'Email',    type: 'email',    extra: 'email: string',                group: 'Links' },
  { name: 'HashTag',  type: 'hashTag',  extra: 'hashtag: string',              group: 'Links' },

  { name: 'Quote', type: 'quote', extra: 'quotedUserId: string?', group: 'Content' },

  { name: 'Attachment', type: 'attachment', extra: 'fileName: string, fileSize: number, contentType: string, width?: number, height?: number, thumbHash?: string', group: 'Content' },

  { name: 'SystemCallStarted', type: 'systemCallStarted', extra: 'callerId: string?, callId: string?',                           group: 'System' },
  { name: 'SystemCallEnded',   type: 'systemCallEnded',   extra: 'callerId: string?, callId: string?, durationSeconds: number?',  group: 'System' },
  { name: 'SystemCallTimeout', type: 'systemCallTimeout', extra: 'callerId: string?, callId: string?',                            group: 'System' },
  { name: 'SystemUserJoined',  type: 'systemUserJoined',  extra: 'userId: string?, inviterId?: string',                           group: 'System' },
];

const groups = ['Formatting', 'Mentions', 'Links', 'Content', 'System'];
---

<DocsLayout title="Message Entities — Argon Bot API" current="/guides/message-entities/" toc={[
  { id: "how-entities-work", title: "How Entities Work" },
  { id: "entity-types", title: "Entity Types" },
]}>
  <div class="animate-fade-in-up">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-2">Message Entities</h1>
    <p class="text-text-secondary text-lg">Rich text formatting, mentions, links, attachments, and system events — all expressed as entity spans within message text.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-10 space-y-12 animate-fade-in-up-delay-1">

    <!-- How entities work -->
    <section>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <Type class="size-5 text-accent" />
        <h2 id="how-entities-work" class="text-xl font-semibold">How Entities Work <a href="#how-entities-work" class="anchor-link">#</a></h2>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <p class="text-text-secondary">
          Every message has a plain <code class="bg-oled-elevated px-1 py-0.5 rounded font-mono text-[11px]">text</code> field plus an optional <code class="bg-oled-elevated px-1 py-0.5 rounded font-mono text-[11px]">entities</code> array.
          Each entity marks a span of the text with a <code class="bg-oled-elevated px-1 py-0.5 rounded font-mono text-[11px]">type</code> discriminator and offset/length.
          Extra fields are present only when relevant for the entity type — all other fields are <code class="bg-oled-elevated px-1 py-0.5 rounded font-mono text-[11px]">null</code>.
        </p>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-5">
          <h4 class="text-xs font-semibold text-text-muted uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Base fields (all entities)</h4>
          <div class="type-grid">
            <div class="type-grid-header">
              <span>Field</span>
              <span>Type</span>
            </div>
            <div class="type-grid-row">
              <span class="type-property font-mono text-[12px]">type</span>
              <span class="font-mono text-[12px]"><span class="type-keyword">string</span></span>
            </div>
            <div class="type-grid-row">
              <span class="type-property font-mono text-[12px]">offset</span>
              <span class="font-mono text-[12px]"><span class="type-keyword">number</span></span>
            </div>
            <div class="type-grid-row">
              <span class="type-property font-mono text-[12px]">length</span>
              <span class="font-mono text-[12px]"><span class="type-keyword">number</span></span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-5">
          <h4 class="text-xs font-semibold text-text-muted uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Example — bold + mention</h4>
          <div class="code-block text-[12px]">
            <pre set:html={`<span class="text-text-muted">// "Hello **world**!" with bold on "world"</span>
{
  <span class="text-accent-2">"text"</span>: <span class="text-accent-2">"Hello world!"</span>,
  <span class="text-accent-2">"entities"</span>: [
    {
      <span class="text-accent-2">"type"</span>: <span class="text-accent-2">"bold"</span>,
      <span class="text-accent-2">"offset"</span>: <span class="type-keyword">6</span>,
      <span class="text-accent-2">"length"</span>: <span class="type-keyword">5</span>
    }
  ]
}

<span class="text-text-muted">// Mention entity — only userId is populated</span>
{
  <span class="text-accent-2">"type"</span>: <span class="text-accent-2">"mention"</span>,
  <span class="text-accent-2">"offset"</span>: <span class="type-keyword">0</span>,
  <span class="text-accent-2">"length"</span>: <span class="type-keyword">6</span>,
  <span class="text-accent-2">"userId"</span>: <span class="text-accent-2">"d3b07384-..."</span>
}`} />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Entity types by group -->
    {groups.map(group => {
      const items = entities.filter(e => e.group === group);
      const icon = group === 'Formatting' ? Sparkles
        : group === 'Mentions' ? AtSign
        : group === 'Links' ? Link
        : group === 'Content' ? Paperclip
        : Phone;

      return (
        <section>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <icon class="size-5 text-accent" />
            <h2 id="entity-types" class="text-xl font-semibold">{group} <a href="#entity-types" class="anchor-link">#</a></h2>
          </div>

          <div class="glass rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
            <div class="type-grid">
              <div class="type-grid-header">
                <span>Entity Type</span>
                <span>Extra Fields</span>
              </div>
              {items.map(entity => (
                <div class="type-grid-row">
                  <span class="font-mono text-[12px]">
                    <span class="type-enum">&quot;{entity.type}&quot;</span>
                  </span>
                  <span class="font-mono text-[12px] text-text-secondary">
                    {entity.extra
                      ? entity.extra.split(', ').map((f: string, i: number) => {
                          const [name, typ] = f.split(': ');
                          return (
                            <>
                              {i > 0 && <span class="text-text-faint">, </span>}
                              <span class="type-property">{name}</span>
                              <span class="text-text-faint">: </span>
                              <span class="type-keyword">{typ}</span>
                            </>
                          );
                        })
                      : <span class="text-text-faint">—</span>
                    }
                  </span>
                </div>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      );
    })}

    <!-- Notes -->
    <section>
      <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-5 border-l-2 border-accent">
        <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-2">Notes</h4>
        <ul class="text-sm text-text-secondary space-y-2">
          <li>Entities can overlap — for example, bold and italic on the same span.</li>
          <li>System entities (<code class="bg-oled-elevated px-1 py-0.5 rounded font-mono text-[11px]">systemCall*</code>, <code class="bg-oled-elevated px-1 py-0.5 rounded font-mono text-[11px]">systemUserJoined</code>) are created by the server. Bots cannot send system entities.</li>
          <li>Attachment entities contain file metadata (<code class="bg-oled-elevated px-1 py-0.5 rounded font-mono text-[11px]">fileName</code>, <code class="bg-oled-elevated px-1 py-0.5 rounded font-mono text-[11px]">fileSize</code>, <code class="bg-oled-elevated px-1 py-0.5 rounded font-mono text-[11px]">contentType</code>). No internal file IDs are exposed.</li>
          <li>Entity objects are <strong>flattened</strong> — all possible extra fields exist on the same type, but only the fields relevant to the entity's <code class="bg-oled-elevated px-1 py-0.5 rounded font-mono text-[11px]">type</code> are non-null.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
</DocsLayout>
